headline: Bel Fuse (BELFB) Beats Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Bel Fuse (BELFB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +17.86% and +2.49%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Lean into the ride on the open road or closed track with zūmo XT3 from Garmin
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced its newest and most advanced motorcycle-focused GPS equipment, zūmo® XT3. Designed to endure handlebar vibration, bumpy rides and extreme weather, the device features a bright, glove-friendly display with either a 4.7 or 6-inch high-resolution screen. The new live lean angle gauge allows riders to see how far they've leaned on each turn in real time. Ride summary data is available to view after each adventure in the Tread® smartphone app.
